node.title: Man's body pulled from Wellington harbour
node.description: A passerby saw the body in the water and pulled him ashore.
node.content: ["A passerby has pulled a man's body from Wellington harbour.", "Police say emergency services were called to reports of a sudden death in central Wellington this morning.", "Stuff reports the man was recovered from Wellington harbour near the Star Boating Club after a passerby saw the body in the water and pulled him ashore.", "\"A 47-year-old man was retrieved from Wellington Harbour at about 7am and has died at the scene,\" police said in a statement.", "\"Police are making enquiries in relation to the death on behalf of the coroner.\""]
